summary: We know Peter was in band but what instrument did he play? Did he choose the tuba because it looked like fun and then instantly...
body: We know Peter was in band but what instrument did he play? Did he choose the tuba because it looked like fun and then instantly regret it because it was so heavy? Was everyone like ??? when he could suddenly carry it with no problem? Did he get stuck with the triangle because he’s the Science Boi and knows nothing about music and was only in band because Ned was? Was he the first chair trumpet that got all the solos and all the other trumpets hated? Was he one of the 200 clarinet players who are only in band to boost their college apps or was he in the bass clarinet clique? Was he That One Kid in jazz band that played Careless Whisper on his saxophone in between every class in the halls? Did he somehow convince the band director to let him play the kazoo?

summary: Guys You Knew/Dated in High School: Spider-Man(s) Edition
body:
Guys You Knew/Dated in High School: Spider-Man(s) Edition

Tobey Maguire: The kid who got beat up in the hallway and cried when the class’s pet fish died in bio because he got too attached. Doesn’t understand any of the jokes he hears and finds it literally impossible to function when in the presence of a female. Uses horrible pick up lines from cheesy movies that everyone watched because their dads forced them to. Stood up to the school bully one time and now nobody is quite sure what to think about him.

Andrew Garfield: That one guy you and everyone else dated that wouldn’t fucking quit touching your hair. Thought he had a cool hipster aesthetic but he’s really just an off-brand skater boy who carries a camera around to take pics of the “unassuming” people he sees on the subway to put on his subpar photography Instagram. Wears ugly scarves and carries a man bag for the aesthetic. Says “whoa” and “dude” way too much for anyone else to be comfortable and goes through more hair gel than he can afford.

Tom Holland: That freshman you probably pitty-danced with at homecoming because he asked you and he was already too short to reach the other girl’s shoulders. Once got shoved into a locker by the school bully and was rescued by the janitor after class was over. Tripped and dropped his science project into a puddle right outside the school. Bitches to his one and only friend about how life just isn’t fair and still bounces on the bed like a five year old. Says he’s related to someone famous to try to score points with the ladies.

summary:
Can you imagine Tony in Homecoming between when he took the suit from Peter and when he gave it back 
He was probably going up...
body:
Can you imagine Tony in Homecoming between when he took the suit from Peter and when he gave it back

He was probably going up to Pepper everyday like

“Was that too much? Should I not have taken the suit away? No he could’ve died! I should’ve taken it away! But he’s a good kid! I don’t wanna act like Howard. And He was just trying to help. I don’t know maybe I should give it back? No no your right your right I’m not gonna give it back…

Ok I’m gonna go work on his new suit for when he becomes an Avenger.”
